[SN]TITLE[SN]
Newport protected by new order on begging and alcohol

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
People begging and drinking alcohol in the street are among those being targeted in a police crackdown in Newport.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Street-based charity fundraisers will also be targeted from Sunday.
